{"tid":2499781,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"郝德傑道豪宅情侶互毆　兩敗俱傷同惹官非","createTime":"2021-04-22T06:45:09.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-22T06:51:57.000Z","uid":3090,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"7503cf4318a7214ff19b963eb4544e04963ea53f","tid":2499781,"uid":3090,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-22T06:45:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmWcxb4QX2DjCahr4RcjYKtDRSfcY9AVuXcF88Nskt3ftj?filename=enjZHKy.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FenjZHKy.jpg&h=9314d28e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n警方到場調查。(沈厚錚攝)<br />\n<br />\n長沙灣郝德傑道2號郝德傑山一豪宅單位，在今日(22日)凌晨2時47分，一名外籍女子向保安員求助，指遭男友襲擊，保安員於是代為報警。<br />\n<br />\n警方接報到場，在涉案單位內發現該名外籍女子頭及手部受傷，而其男友則胸口受傷，屋內散落一堆玻璃碎片。兩人由救護員即場包紮後送院作進一步治理。<br />\n<br />\n警員亦緊隨到院了解事發經過，初步相信該名22歲持護照俄羅斯籍女子曾毀壞男友的電話及一個玻璃杯，及後亦以玻璃碎片割傷男友，惟遭對方拳毆還擊。警方以涉嫌「傷人」及「刑事毀壞」拘捕該名女子，而其姓張(42歲)男友亦涉「普通襲擊」被捕。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20210422/mobile/bkn-20210422040519292-0422_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20210422%2Fmobile%2Fbkn-20210422040519292-0422_00822_001.html&d=tbI6yIPhVaIexgVZB5ClnUYnXQRGGZgEWtwyrMN1cgk%3D&h=3482dd70\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20210422/mobile/bkn-20210422040519292-0422_00822_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"601a1eec1e162816b78e34072dfbfd551badf858","tid":2499781,"uid":50041,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-22T06:49:20.000Z","msg":"戰鬥民族係唔同D,正常港女俾有錢佬包應該唔敢咁惡"},{"pid":"bfcc8e5286ca364b55698a08c054a7a85a78de46","tid":2499781,"uid":370409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-22T06:51:57.000Z","msg":"42歲男<br />\n22歲女"}]}